Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.50,地名,,0000,0000,0000,,（奥马哈海滩，绿D区）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:34.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别挡住跳板，三十秒后登陆，愿主保佑你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Clear the ramp! 30 seconds! May God be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:39.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷右舷听着，尽快攻占炮台\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Port side and starboard side stick!Move fast and clear those mortar holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大家尽量分散\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I want to see plenty of beach between men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:46.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,五个人就容易成为目标，一个人则能躲开\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Five men is a juicy opportunity. One man is a waste of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:50.74,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别让沙子堵塞枪口，小心行事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Keep the sand out of your weapons! Keep those actions clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,在滩头上见\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'll see you on the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:28.98,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,避开弹坑，分成左右两列\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Clear the mortar hole! Right and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,到旁边去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Over the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.79,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,从左右方下水\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Port and starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Thank yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.44,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，怎么办\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What now, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，现在怎么办\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I said, What the hell do we do now, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:34.04,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,米勒上尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain Miller! Captain Miller!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:39.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,米勒上尉     霍瓦特中士\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Captain Miller!   - Sergeant Horvath!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:43.33,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你的弟兄攻上滩头，快\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Move your men off the beach! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.19,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我命令，跟着我冲\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Okay, you guys, get on my ass! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:52.43,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，集合点在哪里     总之不是这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Sir! What's the rallying point?    - Anywhere but here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:08.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办，长官     快攻上海堤\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What now, sir?   - The seawall, move up to the seawall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:12.45,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下来     先攻占滩头再说\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Sir, I'm staying!   - Clear the beach to make way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.25,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,走出去就死定了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This is all we've got between us and the Almighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:20.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这滩头的每一处都被瞄准了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Every inch of this beach has been pre-sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.33,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,留下来必死无疑\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You stay here, you're dead men!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.54,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mama, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,伏下来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Stay down, stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:56.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么部队     104师的医疗营\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What are you guys?   - 104th Medical Battalion,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:12:00.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来设立医疗站的     丢掉这废物\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- We're here to set up field operations.   - Get rid of that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:04.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,拿起武器跟我来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Grab yourselves some weapons and follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我中弹了     布格斯\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I'm hit!   - Briggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.75,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,医护兵\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:24.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，我中弹了     医护兵\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I'm hit low! God!   - Medic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是海军抢滩大队\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Navy Beach Battalion, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我得清除这些障碍给坦克开路\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I've got to clear these obstacles. Make holes for the tanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:33.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,装甲车都掉到海里了     长官，这是命令\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- All the armour is floundering at sea.   - Orders, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.74,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,到别处去，这里交给我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Go somewhere else! I'm clearing this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，布格斯\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Come on, Briggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.91,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,医护兵\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,医护兵\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.02,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,快走，快\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，快\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Come on, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:58.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,海岸后勤工作队装甲车都无法登岸\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Shore party! No armour has made it ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:03.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,滩头上都没有DD坦克，D1缺口还没打开\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We've got no DD tanks on the beach.Dog One is not open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是谁指挥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Who's in command here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.23,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，是你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You are, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:13.76,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,霍瓦特中士，你认得这是哪里吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sergeant Horvath? Do you recognize where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是原定的集合点，但却没有支援部队\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Where we're supposed to be, but no one else is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.71,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都走散了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Nobody's where they're supposed to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:22.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,海岸后勤工作队\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Shore party!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:25.65,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,第一波攻击无效，无法攻占海滩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}First wave ineffective! We do not hold the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.91,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,重复，无法攻占海滩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Say again, we do not hold the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:34.25,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都混在一起了，这里有F、A和G连的弟兄\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We're mixed up! We've got people from Fox,Able and George companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:38.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,和海军爆破队员及陆战队长\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Plus, we got some Navy demo guys and a beachmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:42.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,海岸后勤工作队\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Shore party, Shore party!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:51.37,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}CAT-F, CAT-F, CA...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾报到     有看到别人吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Reiben here.   - Seen anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,只有杰克森     梅利西报到\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Jackson,but that's it.   - Mellish here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.81,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,卡帕佐，德佛里斯特和韦德在后面\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Caparzo! We've got DeForest back there with Wade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:08.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他严重失血，韦德说他没救了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}D.'s hurt so bad he's sprung a hundred leaks! Wade says he's used up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:13.75,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去救其他人吧     我们走吧，他是军医\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Move on to somebody you can help.   - Let go, he's a battalion surgeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:20.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去叫他     韦德\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Get his attention!   - Wade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:23.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德     韦德\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Wade!   - Wade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:27.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德，别这么做，太危险了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Wade, don't do it! It's too risky, too risky, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:30.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,快滚回来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get your ass back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.18,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,把他带回来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get him off the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:36.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我办到了，我们替他止住血了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I've got it! We've stopped the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.62,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:42.45,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋，赶尽杀绝\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Just give us a fucking chance, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:45.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德，走吧     你这个混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Wade, come on!   - You son of a fucking cocksucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:49.10,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德，是梅利西，韦德\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Wade, it's Mellish. Wade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，找到米勒了，走吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Let's move! We found Miller! Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fuck it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,伏下\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get down, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你们几个吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This is all? This is all that's made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:09.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被分散了，一定还有人的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We got scattered pretty bad. There's bound to be more of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.81,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不够\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:14.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,D1缺口是在右边还是左边\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Dog One exit. It's the cut to the right, or was it left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:18.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不，维尔维里在左边，这里才是D1缺口\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}No. Vierville is to the left. This is Dog One.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:24.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在痛宰我们，根本没有机会战斗，不公平\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}They're killing us and we don't have a fucking chance! That ain't fair!
