Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.85,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:19.45,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,迫击炮来了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mortars incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一支\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}One more, give me one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，痛死我了，我快要死了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Oh, my God, it hurts! I'm going to die!
