Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:53.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会死的，别看，没事的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You're not going to die. You're fine. Just don't look at it. Don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:57.45,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,用爆破筒来攻击，让开\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Bangalores! Clear the shingle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:00.10,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,对准沙坑     对准沙坑\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Fire in the hole!   - Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,对准沙坑\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:06.03,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,对准沙坑\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fire in the hole!
