Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,一般处理\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.18,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,优先处理\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.18,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He is gone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:13.46,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋，过去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Son of a bitch! Get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.70,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，我动不了     梅利西，刺刀给我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Fuck,I can't move!   - Mellish,give me your bayonet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,中士\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:40.12,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,两挺MG-42机枪，两支迫击炮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Two MG-42s, two mortars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.19,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,在前方20码，左边30码\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Add 20, left 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:49.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那有掩护物，若装甲车登陆后会是最好的发射位置\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}There's defilade, but it's a good firing position if we can land the armour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得打开这个缺口\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We've got to get this draw open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:57.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾、梅利西，上吧，找到掩护就猛烈开火\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Reiben, Mellish! Let's get in the war! Take cover and put fire on that crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:02.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,戴维斯、德伯纳多、杨、瓦克，快准备\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Davis, DeBernardo, Young, Valk! Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,开火\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Covering fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.02,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.57,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军的炮火很厉害\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It's a goddam firing squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:29.58,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要逃出这里，只有这样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It's the only way we can get everybody out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:34.05,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,肖特、佩森、麦唐纳、帕克斯，你们是下一组\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Short, Payton, McDonald, Parkes! You're next!
