Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:44.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:49.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,快点     上，该死\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Come on, come on, come on!  - Go, God damm it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克森     是，长官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Jackson.   - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:09.61,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,看见那弹坑吗，在那里应该能躲开机枪的攻击\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}See that impact crater? should give you defilade from the machine gun position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:13.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,躲进去好好表现枪法，等我的命令\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get in there and give me some fire discipline. Wait for my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:35.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,若你妈看见你这样会很担忧的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}If your mother saw you do that, she'd be very upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:38.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你就是我妈呢\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I thought you were my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:40.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别远离我，上帝\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Be not Thou far from me, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:50.75,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,主啊，很抱歉我曾经激怒你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Oh, my God. I am heartily sorry for having offended Thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:55.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我对此深感懊悔，请听我的祷告\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I detest my sins for having offended Thee, O Lord. Listen to me, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:06.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,赐我力量，助我抗敌\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}All my strength! Haste Thee to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:24.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,D1缺口打开了，往这边走\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Dog One exit, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.52,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大家反攻\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We're in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:30.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:12.63,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾     去吧，中士\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Reiben.   - Go, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:14.47,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Reiben!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:44.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，多里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Come on, Doyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:48.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,中士\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:55.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,多里，打开喷火器\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Flame! Doyle, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:03.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪，让他们吃吃苦头\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Don't shoot! Let them burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.58,0:24:21.70,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,右边\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}On the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.22,0:24:27.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你们一起死吧，混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'll give you "comrade", you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.75,0:24:31.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,小心，转过去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Look out! Turn around, turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.78,0:24:54.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去干掉他们\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Flush them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.48,0:25:02.85,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,停火，住手\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Cease fire, cease fire! Cut it out, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.05,0:25:04.49,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,停火\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.16,0:25:09.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这是SC第3队，重复，D1缺口已经打开\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sugar Cane, Sugar Charlie Three. Say again, Dog One is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.43,0:25:13.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,派出推土机，我在这里等待配合侧翼\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Send in the dozers. I'm waiting here to tie in my flanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.13,0:25:15.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.77,0:25:22.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，抱歉，我听不懂你在说什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What? I'm sorry, I can't understand what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.85,0:25:32.37,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What did he say, what did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.58,0:25:35.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我洗过手准备吃饭了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Look, I washed for supper!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.22,0:25:41.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谁有火箭筒，真该死\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Who's got a bazooka,Goddammit
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.20,0:25:52.43,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，你看，是希特勒青年团小刀\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hey, Fish. Look at this, a Hitler Youth knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.17,0:25:56.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是犹太面包刀了，对吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}And now it's a Shabbat challah cutter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.01,0:26:08.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别停下来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Keep it moving!
