Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.97,0:27:11.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,好惨烈的景象\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That's quite a view.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.79,0:27:13.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.07,0:27:17.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,很惨烈\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Quite a view.
