Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.80,0:53:15.56,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大家别冒险出去，那枪手枪法很厉害\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I wouldn't venture out there, fellas. This sniper's got talent!
