Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.86,0:53:47.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,扶我起来，我可以走路\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Help me up. I can walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.03,0:53:49.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,卡帕佐，别动\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Caparzo, stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.55,0:54:04.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,两格，风向偏左\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Two clicks. Left wind.
