Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.80,0:54:19.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，看到他吗，他怎么了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain, can you see him? How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.56,0:54:21.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德，别乱来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Wade, you stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.87,0:54:24.03,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，他哪里中枪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Where is he shot, Captain?
