Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.31,0:54:30.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，躺下来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Damn it! Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.88,0:54:35.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了，你中了枪要我照顾吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What's the matter with you? Am I going to take care of you if you get hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.71,0:54:37.54,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，过来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fish, come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.74,0:54:41.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,卡帕佐，躺下来别动\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Carpy, put your head down! Why can't you put your head down?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.90,0:54:53.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,神啊，我信靠你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Oh, my God, I trust in Thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.27,0:54:59.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别让我蒙羞，别让敌人战胜我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Let me not be ashamed. Let not my enemies triumph over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.28,0:55:12.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,抄下来，替我寄出去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Copy it. Copy it and send it for me.
