Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.29,0:55:26.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,给我爸的，沾了血，笨蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It's... It's to my dad. It's got blood on it, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.42,0:55:57.76,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了，伏下\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We got him. Stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.64,0:56:10.04,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,伤得很重吗     胸口中弹，或许肺被打中了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- How bad is it?   - Chest, maybe lung shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.32,0:56:28.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,把那台30毫米大炮放到街上\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get that.30 up the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.52,0:56:36.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,报告情况     上面安全\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Detail!   - Clear, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.27,0:56:37.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,下面安全\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Clear, down!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.75,0:56:55.31,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,早就说过不能带孩子\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That's why we can't take children.
