Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.53,0:57:15.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,召集弟兄，在广场西北角集合\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Gather your men. We'll form up at the northwest corner of the square.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.94,0:57:17.50,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克森     是，长官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Jackson.   - Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.71,0:57:22.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利西，去检查那座塔，尽快回来，快去吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mellish. Check the tower, hustle back here. Right now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.19,0:57:36.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fuck Ryan!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.44,0:57:50.63,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,打雷     闪电，进来吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Thunder!    - Flash! Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.28,0:57:57.50,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找汉米尔上尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hey, guys. We're looking for Captain Hamill.
