Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.71,0:58:02.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走，提防狙击手\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Go easy. Watch for snipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.32,0:58:06.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.74,0:58:24.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米，叫汉米尔上尉过来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Jimmy T. Go and find Captain Hamill. Bring him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.10,0:58:29.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，上面吗     我怎么知道，自己去找\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What? Up there?   - How should I know? Go and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.27,0:58:31.03,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Thank you, you moron.
