Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.48,0:58:43.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把石子倒出来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Let me get this goddam hitchhiker out of my boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.29,0:58:57.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器     立刻放下\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Put your weapons down!   - Drop them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.15,0:59:02.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我会开枪的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.14,0:59:04.54,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Drop, drop 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.71,0:59:09.44,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻放下武器\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Put 'em down!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.06,0:59:26.65,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上面安全了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Clear, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.87,0:59:34.23,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Shit, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.44,0:59:36.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上面安全了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Clear, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.94,0:59:38.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,下面也安全了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Clear, down!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.82,0:59:52.25,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子够让人变老了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Enough to make you old.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.62,0:59:54.82,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Let's hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.97,1:00:08.77,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,101师前导部队的汉米尔     第二突击队的米勒\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Hamill, Pathfinders 101st.   - Miller, 2nd Rangers.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.97,1:00:11.50,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.71,1:00:14.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找二等兵瑞恩，他是你的属下\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We're looking for a Private Ryan. He's part of your outfit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.38,1:00:16.40,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能找到他吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Any chance that you policed him up?
