Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.15,1:00:24.12,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,还死了一位队员\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Not to mention one of our men.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.32,1:00:28.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉，把火箭筒调换到右边的路旁\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Lieutenant! Redeploy that bazooka to the right side of the road.
