Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.95,1:00:52.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我早说他是个混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I told you he was an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.05,1:00:57.71,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵瑞恩报到     稍息\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Private Ryan reporting as ordered.   - At ease.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.92,1:01:01.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,第二突击队的米勒上尉有话跟你说\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain Miller, 2nd Rangers, wants a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.96,1:01:05.12,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这边来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This way.
