Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.61,1:01:19.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵，有个坏消息要告诉你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Private, I'm afraid I have some bad news for you.
