Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.72,1:01:38.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我就直说吧，你的兄弟死了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}...so I'll just say it. Your brothers are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.39,1:01:44.02,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们奉命来找你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We have orders to come and get you...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.23,1:01:46.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你可以回家了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}...because you're going home.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.38,1:02:02.47,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，我兄弟死了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Oh, my God! My brothers are dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.46,1:02:14.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我本想带他们去钓鱼的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I was going to take them fishing when we got home.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.84,1:02:32.04,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，詹姆斯，真是不知该说什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm so sorry, James. I can't tell you how much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.25,1:02:37.65,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是怎样死的     阵亡\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- How did they die?   - They were killed in action.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.72,1:02:41.85,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没有可能\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That can't be.
