Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.24,1:02:56.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,爱阿华州的詹姆斯·法兰西斯·瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}James Francis Ryan from lowa?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.04,1:03:00.44,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我是明尼苏达州的詹姆斯·腓德利克·瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}James Frederick Ryan, Minnesota.
