Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.03,1:03:30.20,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我在离开前才刚给他们写信，我要回家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I just wrote them a letter before I left. I've got to get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.41,1:03:35.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我要立刻回家，我想回家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I've got to get home right now. I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.88,1:03:37.24,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的瑞恩在哪里呢     不知道\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Where is our Ryan?   - Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.45,1:03:41.47,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟指挥官联络一下吗     瑞恩隶属于什么单位\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Are you in touch with your CO?   - What unit's Ryan in?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.68,1:03:45.64,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,506团的B连     那个断脚的家伙是506团的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Baker Company, 506th.   - The guy with the broken foot's in 506th.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.85,1:03:48.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜是C连吧     你猜\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Charlie, I think.   - You think?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.52,1:03:52.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩，我不知道，天啊\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Ryan? Don't know... Man!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.49,1:03:54.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在哪里降落     维尔维里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Where was your dropzone?   - Vierville.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.16,1:03:57.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,维尔维里，那怎么会到这来的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Vierville? How did you end up here?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.10,1:04:01.19,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长，C-47受到猛烈的攻击\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You got me, sir. The C-47 took heavy fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.40,1:04:03.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,机师拼命闪避炮火\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Pilot went crazy turning every which way.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.11,1:04:08.24,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,跳伞时炮火更猛，情况混乱，我就来了这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We took more fire in the drop. It got messy. I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.44,1:04:11.54,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我没见过我的队友，天知道他们在哪里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I haven't seen a single guy from my stick. God knows where they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.75,1:04:15.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有B连的人谈到空降区在哪吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Did anybody from Baker Company talk about where the dropzone was?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.58,1:04:18.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，但大家的集合点一样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}No, but they had the same rallying point as us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.09,1:04:20.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,指出来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.86,1:04:27.35,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很累，在这里休息三小时，入夜后出发\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}My men are beat. We'll hold up here for three hours and pull out after dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.56,1:04:30.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这镇上有三星级饭店什么的吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Got anything left in this town, like a three-star hotel?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.47,1:04:33.56,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有干净的床单、枕头和客房服务吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Something with clean sheets, soft pillows and room service?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.77,1:04:37.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,舒适的教堂怎么样     也好\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- How about a nice, comfy church?   - We'll take that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.41,1:04:40.20,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么消息，战况怎么样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What have you heard? How is it all falling together?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.41,1:04:44.57,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们攻下了滩头堡，但蒙蒂却慢条斯理的进军康城\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We got the beachhead secured,but Monty's taking his time moving on Caen.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.78,1:04:48.81,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要他准备好我们才能撤军     大家高估他了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- We can't pull out'til he's ready,so...   - That guy's overrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.02,1:04:52.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意     要拿下康城才能攻下圣罗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- No argument here.   - You take Caen to take Saint-L8.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.72,1:04:56.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要攻下瓦隆尼先要拿下圣罗     瓦隆尼之后是瑟堡\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- You gotta take St-L8 to take Valognes.   - Valognes,you've got Cherbourg.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.52,1:04:59.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑟堡之后是巴黎     最后是柏林\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Cherbourg,you've got Paris.   - Paris,you've got Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.19,1:05:02.63,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就能坐大船回家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}And then that big boat home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.90,1:05:09.60,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里能帮到我很多，但我了解你的任务\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I could really use you around here, but I understand what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.80,1:05:13.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗     我也有几个兄弟\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- You do?   - I've got a couple of brothers myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.14,1:05:16.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样     祝你好运\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Oh.   - Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.48,1:05:18.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢     不，我是说真的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Thank you.   - No, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.18,1:05:22.24,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,找到他，带他回家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Find him. Get him home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.09,1:05:32.18,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手怎么了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What's with your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.46,1:05:35.76,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.00,1:05:39.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,在朴次茅斯上船后就是这样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It started in Portsmouth when we went down for embarkation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.13,1:05:44.76,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会这样     你该找别的工作\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- It comes and goes.   - You have to find yourself a new job.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.97,1:05:47.60,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这工作不适合你了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This one doesn't seem to agree with you any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.55,1:05:55.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.52,1:06:01.45,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,什么     没什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What?   - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.66,1:06:04.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,在安济奥那小子叫什么名字\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What was the name of that kid at Anzio?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.59,1:06:07.58,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,用手倒立走路那个\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The one who walked on his hands
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.80,1:06:10.56,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,唱着空中飞人之歌那个吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and was singing that song about the man on the flying trapeze?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.77,1:06:13.56,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是维驰奥     维驰奥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Vecchio.   - Vecchio!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.24,1:06:22.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,对，他是个笨蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah, Vecchio. He was a goofy kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.11,1:06:29.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢在别人的外套上尿出一个“V”字，代表维驰奥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I remember he used to pee a "v" on everybody's jackets. For "vecchio".
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.62,1:06:32.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,代表胜利     维驰奥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- For victory.   - Vecchio.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.29,1:06:38.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他长得很矮     他是侏儒吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- He was so short.   - He was a midget, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.16,1:06:42.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那他怎么能当上突击队队员的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah, how did he get to be a Ranger?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.16,1:06:45.76,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他的脚被打断了，所以用手走路\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He got shot in the foot once, walking on his hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.97,1:06:49.77,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,走得很快\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He could walk faster on his hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.97,1:06:52.84,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,跑得更加快\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He could run faster on his hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.61,1:06:59.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,维驰奥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Vecchio. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.98,1:07:03.25,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,卡帕佐\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Caparzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.82,1:07:14.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,每当一位弟兄死去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You see, when you end up killing one of your men
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.90,1:07:19.60,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,就要告诉自己，这样能拯救\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}you tell yourself it happened so you could save the lives of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.80,1:07:24.03,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,二、三、四或十条人命\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}two, three, or ten others.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.27,1:07:27.71,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是一百人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Maybe 100 others.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.41,1:07:34.31,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我当指挥时有多少部下阵亡吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Do you know how many men I've lost under my command?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.52,1:07:36.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,多少     九十四个\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- How many?   - 94.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.95,1:07:43.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但那代表我救了十倍那么多的人吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}But that means I've saved the lives of ten times that many, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.93,1:07:48.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是二十倍\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Maybe even 20, right? 20 times as many?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.34,1:07:57.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这么简单\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}And that's how simple it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.74,1:08:02.90,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样把任务与属下之间\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That's how you rationalise making the choice
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.11,1:08:06.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,所做的选择合理化\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}between the mission and the men.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.38,1:08:09.25,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但这次任务正是救人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Except that this time the mission is a man.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.99,1:08:15.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这个瑞恩最好值得我们去救\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This Ryan had better be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.29,1:08:20.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他回家后最好能行医救人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He'd better go home and cure some disease
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.20,1:08:25.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,或是发明长寿灯泡\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}or invent a longer-lasting light-bulb or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.57,1:08:30.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我想十个瑞恩也抵不了一个卡帕佐或维驰奥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}For the truth is that I wouldn't trade ten Ryans for one Vecchio or Caparzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.20,1:08:32.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.08,1:08:37.60,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，又来了     长官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Look, there it goes again.   - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.08,1:08:40.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.19,1:08:49.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,两小时后出发，小睡一会吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We'll move out in two hours. Why don't you get some sleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.93,1:08:53.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他怎么能做到的     什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I don't know how he does it.   - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.13,1:08:56.65,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,如此熟睡，你看\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Falls asleep like that. Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.86,1:08:59.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他躺下就睡着了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The guy's lights-out the minute his head hits the pack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.03,1:09:03.37,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,因为问心无愧     有句话怎么说\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Clear conscience.   - What's that saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.57,1:09:05.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,神与我们同在，那谁与敌军同在\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}God's on our side, who could be on theirs?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.07,1:09:09.04,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,若神与我们同在，谁会是我们的对手\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"If God be for us, who could be against us?"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.24,1:09:11.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不错，我说了什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah, what did I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.55,1:09:15.71,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,想睡着的话保持清醒就行了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The trick to falling asleep is trying to stay awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.92,1:09:17.58,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么，韦德\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}How is that, Wade?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.79,1:09:22.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈当实习医师时习惯在夜间工作\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}When my mother was an intern she used to work through the night
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.92,1:09:24.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,白天睡觉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and sleep through the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.33,1:09:28.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,只有她回家我们才能聊天\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The only time we talked was when she'd get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.86,1:09:35.79,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我总会躺着，尽量保持清醒，但从没成功过\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I used to lie in bed and stay awake as long as I could,but it never worked
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.00,1:09:40.30,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我越不想睡就越快睡着\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}because the harder I tried the faster I'd fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.51,1:09:43.74,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但在家里没关系，因为妈会回家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That wouldn't have mattered in my house.Ma would've come home,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.94,1:09:49.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,把我弄醒，聊到天亮，聊天时她总是不知道累\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}shook me awake,chatted me up 'til dawn.She was never too tired to talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.28,1:09:52.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,也许她在那个时候才有机会说话\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That's probably the only time she could get a word in.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.32,1:10:00.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的是有时她下班时间早了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Funny thing is,sometimes she would come home early
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.13,1:10:03.49,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我会假装睡着了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and I'd pretend to be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.70,1:10:07.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谁，你妈吗     对\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Who, your mum?   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.07,1:10:13.47,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,她会站在门口看着我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}She'd stand in the doorway looking at me,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.67,1:10:16.54,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我就闭眼装睡\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and I would just keep my eyes shut.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.68,1:10:22.58,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她特地早些回来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}And I knew that she just wanted to find out about my day,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.82,1:10:29.28,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我聊天，问我那天过得怎么样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}that she came home early just to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.13,1:10:36.19,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但我却仍然不动，假装已经熟睡\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}And I still wouldn't move. I'd still pretend to be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.30,1:10:45.64,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道为什么会那样做\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I don't know why I did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.19,1:11:02.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,只有几个小时，闭嘴睡觉吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We've only got a couple of hours. Shut up and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.57,1:11:14.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，长官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain? Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.44,1:11:18.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,下士\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.68,1:11:26.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了，没事吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}How are you doing? Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.21,1:11:29.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,还好，我想这一切对我有益\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah, I think this is all good for me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.85,1:11:34.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗，为什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Really? How is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.46,1:11:42.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“战争能训练判断力，磨练意志”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}'War educates the senses, calls into action the will,"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.03,1:11:46.19,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“增强体格”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"perfects the physical constitution,"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.40,1:11:50.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“人在生死关头的瞬间”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"brings men in such swift and close collision in critical moments"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.34,1:11:52.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“强弱立判”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"that man measures man."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.87,1:11:57.64,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,爱默森也许是这样让自己积极起来的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I guess that's Emerson's way of finding the bright side.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.85,1:12:02.15,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你也有读爱默森啊     一点点\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- You know Emerson, sir?   - I know some.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.95,1:12:10.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，你来自哪里，在战前你是做什么的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}So, where are you from, Captain? What did you do before the war?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.06,1:12:14.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,赌金有多少了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What's the pool up to?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.87,1:12:21.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是三百块吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I think it's around 300, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.47,1:12:26.10,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,等到了五百的时候我就把答案告诉你，平分赌金\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}When it gets up to 500,I'll give you the answer and we'll split the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.31,1:12:28.30,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}How about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.51,1:12:31.91,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你这么想我就有责任建议你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}If that's the way you feel, I feel it's my duty under your command
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.11,1:12:37.02,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,等赌金累积到一千块\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}to suggest that we wait until it gets up to 1,000. I think it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.22,1:12:40.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要是活不了那么久呢，怎么办\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What if we don't live that long?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.72,1:12:46.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,五百     五百也不错\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- 500?   - 500 would be good, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.99,1:12:48.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，长官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.60,1:12:54.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧，下士     是，长官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Get some sleep, Corporal.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.77,1:14:02.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谁有磺胺粉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Who's got sulfa powder?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.57,1:14:09.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,医护兵，我弟兄在流血，需要止血带\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Medic, my buddy's bleeding! He needs a tourniquet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.01,1:14:11.03,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德     什么事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Wade.   - Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.25,1:14:13.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去帮他一下     是\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- See what you can do.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.68,1:14:16.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住，很快就有人来救你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hold on, fellas. It won't be much longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.98,1:14:19.35,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎么样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}How are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.55,1:14:25.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，别担心，医师来了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Alright. You're doing alright, don't worry about it. The Doc's in town.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.99,1:14:30.79,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,放心，29步兵团已突围，很快到这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Don't worry. The 29th Infantry's breaking through. They'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.00,1:14:33.30,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谁有血浆\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Has anybody got plasma?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.50,1:14:35.43,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hey, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.64,1:14:39.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么消息吗     我是德温得中尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Soldier,you want to fill me in?   - Yeah.Lieutenant DeWindt.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.34,1:14:43.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,隶属于第99运兵中队，负责运载300与307滑翔机步兵\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}99th Troop Carrier Squadron carrying in 300th and 307th Glider Infantry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.31,1:14:46.04,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我是飞行员     二等兵\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- This one was mine. I was the pilot.   - Private!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.25,1:14:47.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,22人阵亡     来照顾他\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- 22 men dead.   - Take care of this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.72,1:14:50.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我着陆时没受一点伤，副驾驶却死了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I landed there without a scratch, took my co-pilot's head right off.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.68,1:14:52.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是谁\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.62,1:14:56.82,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们载的士兵第一晚就离开，之后没再见过他们\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The guys we came in with headed off the first night. Haven't seen them since.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.02,1:15:00.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,期间别的士兵三五成群地陆续出现\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}In the meantime other guys keep showing up. One, two, six at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.13,1:15:03.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,然后有军官来把散兵凑成部队\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Then some officer will come along, patch together a mixed unit
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.13,1:15:06.46,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,再次出发作战\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and head off to make trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.67,1:15:10.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找101师506B连的二等兵瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We're looking for a Private Ryan, Baker Company, 506th of the 101st.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.07,1:15:13.23,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这可难倒我了，这里人来人往\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You got me. A lot of guys come in and out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.44,1:15:16.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，到那队人里面找瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham! Check out that squad. See if Ryan's in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.88,1:15:18.61,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，长官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.01,1:15:25.15,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾，闻闻他的腿像不像臭乳酪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Reiben! Smell that leg, right there. Find out if it's south of cheese.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.66,1:15:33.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.89,1:15:36.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,双手放头上\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hands over your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.17,1:15:40.03,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别停下来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.87,1:15:44.63,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我是犹太人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm Jude, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.31,1:15:51.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,无法把他弄出来，我需要一台绞车\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I couldn't pry him out of there. I need a winch.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.28,1:15:52.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.12,1:15:58.35,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是星级军官     是的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Stars.   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.55,1:16:02.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门准将，101空降师的副指挥官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Brigadier General Amend. Deputy Commander, 101st.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.19,1:16:07.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有些天才提议在机舱焊接钢板\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Some genius had the great idea of welding steel plates onto our deck
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.13,1:16:10.49,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,以免地面的炮火伤到上将\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}to keep the General safe from ground fire,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.70,1:16:14.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们到空降前才告诉我们\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}but they forgot to tell me until just before we were getting airborne.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.04,1:16:18.56,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,就像开货运列车飞行般吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That's like trying to fly a freight train. OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.77,1:16:22.40,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,负荷过重，地面炮火又猛烈\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Gross overload. Trim characteristics all shot to hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.61,1:16:25.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我为了保持平衡手几乎都弄断了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I nearly broke both my arms trying to keep her level.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.68,1:16:29.98,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,脱勾时我已经尽力了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}When we released I cut as hard as I could,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.18,1:16:33.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,尝试保持高度，以免失速\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}trying to gain some altitude and keep her from stalling.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.69,1:16:38.56,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,最后像陨石一样掉下来，结果变成这样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We came down like a fucking meteor. And this is how we ended up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.13,1:16:43.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,其他飞机总算顺利着陆\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The others stopped easy enough, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.60,1:16:47.16,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的飞机太重了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We were just too damn heavy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.37,1:16:52.60,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,草地湿滑，而且是下坡\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The grass was wet. Downward slope and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.81,1:16:55.10,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,死了二十二人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}22 guys dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.44,1:17:01.35,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,全为了一个上将吗     一个人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- All that for a general?   - One man.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.22,1:17:06.35,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事经常发生     “苦差”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- There's a lot of that going around.   - "FUBAR."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.22,1:17:09.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“苦差”     “苦差”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- "FUBAR."   - "FUBAR."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.92,1:17:13.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“苦差”     都说对了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- "FUBAR."   - You all got that right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.16,1:17:16.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我在德语字典中查不到“苦差”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I looked it up in a German dictionary. "FUBAR"'s not there.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.06,1:17:19.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，那边也有伞兵\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham! There are more paratroopers out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.80,1:17:22.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去找瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Find out if one of them is Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.34,1:17:25.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里找找看\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You might want to check this out, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.47,1:17:28.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是兵籍牌，多得数不完\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Dog tags. More than I really want to count, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.94,1:17:33.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我已盖过许多尸体\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I've covered a lot of bodies, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.11,1:17:38.81,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克森，从这些开始找吧     是\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Jackson. Start going through those.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.89,1:17:41.05,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.06,1:17:48.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得有那小子吗     如果有我会找到的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Do you think that little prick's in there?   - If he is,I'm going to find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.76,1:17:51.49,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢说那混蛋     我打赌他还活着\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I bet that son of a bitch...   - I've got money saying he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.70,1:17:55.50,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,赌十块我会先找到     来看这里有什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- 10 bucks says I nail him first.   - Let's see what we've got in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.70,1:17:58.57,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你没希望了     你认为他在这里面吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- You mugs don't stand a chance.   - Do you think he's in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.77,1:18:01.40,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,继续找吧     好吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Just keep looking.   - Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.61,1:18:05.31,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,盖瑞·艾尼高、班瑞·比诺、麦克·塞里奥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"Gary lanico", "Ben Rubino", "Mike Cesario"
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.33,1:18:06.81,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是几内亚人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}...All the Guineas are buying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.01,1:18:11.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这名字     维维里·维基，是你的朋友\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Come on, it's not the right name!   - 'Wee Willie Winkie". A buddy of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.22,1:18:14.15,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得找到那混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We've got to find this prick.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.66,1:18:20.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋在哪里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Where's this son of a bitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.63,1:18:22.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别混在一起，分开一点\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Don't mix them up. Keep them in your pile.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.13,1:18:25.43,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道哪些是看过的呢\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}How am I supposed to know who we've got?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.63,1:18:28.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾，闭嘴好吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Why don't you just shut up, Reiben?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.47,1:18:32.70,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别吵架     你不高兴吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Everybody be friends.   - Cranky there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.91,1:18:35.77,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有优胜者了     你说什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I think I've got a winner.   - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.98,1:18:38.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩     瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- "Ryan."   - Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.41,1:18:41.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利西，你看     你简直是天才\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Take a look at that, Mellis.   - You're really a genius.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.15,1:18:46.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这是里恩，是法语名字，知道这是什么意思吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"R-l-E-N-N-E." That's "Rienne" and it's French. Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.89,1:18:49.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,一无所获     什么比三条大\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- It means "nothing".   - What beats three of a kind?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.69,1:18:54.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人全都来自纽约     你总是发牢骚\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I got shit here, all guys from New York.   - You're always bitching.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.26,1:18:56.20,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要帮忙吗     我葫芦\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Do you need a hand?   - I've got a full house.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.40,1:18:59.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了，同花顺\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I've got you beat. Straight flush.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.60,1:19:02.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你偷看我的牌，你作弊\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You're looking at my cards. You're cheating.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.07,1:19:07.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,笨得太离谱了，你识字吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fucking unreal, this guy. Can you read that shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.24,1:19:11.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，你看这可怜的家伙     大概不能防弹吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Jesus, look at this poor bastard!   - I guess they're not bulletproof.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.01,1:19:13.24,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,应该不能\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.45,1:19:17.98,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙没脑袋     跟你的那里一样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I don't like what's between his ears.  - It's like what's between your legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.19,1:19:21.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得没错     杰克森，说得没错\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- We've got to give him that.   - That's not bad for you, Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.82,1:19:24.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我三条     你们干什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I've got three of a kind.   - What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.86,1:19:28.62,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,整个空降师都在看着，这可不是扑克牌\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The whole goddam Airborne's watching. These aren't poker chips.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.83,1:19:31.30,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧     放回去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Alright.   - Put them back in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.06,1:19:57.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他不在这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.23,1:20:04.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们该分头去找吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Maybe we should split into groups?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.90,1:20:07.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,到树林里去叫他的名字\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Just wander the woods calling his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.30,1:20:10.03,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他迟早会听到的，瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He's bound to hear us sooner or later. Ryan!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.24,1:20:13.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，这也不是办法\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That might be a little hard to do, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.01,1:20:20.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,也许本地人见过他，瑞恩，詹姆斯·瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Maybe the locals have seen him. Ryan, James Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.98,1:20:24.64,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩，有人认识101空降师的瑞恩吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Ryan! Anybody know Ryan, 101st Airborne? You know Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.85,1:20:29.75,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是爱阿华州的二等兵瑞恩吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Private James Ryan from lowa? Anybody know a Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.96,1:20:33.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩     阿乔\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- James Ryan!   - Hey, Joe!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.63,1:20:37.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,麦可森不是认识C连的瑞恩吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Doesn't Michaelson pal around with a Ryan from C Company?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.07,1:20:41.33,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是     带他过来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I think so.   - Bring him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.71,1:20:52.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识二等兵瑞恩吗     你要大声一点\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- You know Private Ryan?   - You have to speak up...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.15,1:20:56.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大声一点，我的耳朵不灵光\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You have to speak up, sir! My hearing is not so good!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.55,1:20:59.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,手榴弹在耳朵边爆炸，听力时有时无的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It comes and goes. A grenade went off right by my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.59,1:21:04.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识二等兵瑞恩吗     谁\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Got it. Do you know Private Ryan?   - Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.29,1:21:07.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵瑞恩，詹姆斯·瑞恩     吉米·瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Private Ryan? James Ryan?   - Jimmy Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.99,1:21:10.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·法兰西斯·瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}James. James Francis Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.03,1:21:14.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是詹姆斯·法兰西斯·瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}No, no, no. James Francis Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.23,1:21:17.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,给我纸笔\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Give me a pencil. Something to write on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.50,1:21:18.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，铅笔\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Quick, a pencil!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.31,1:21:23.14,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,小铅笔给你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Here you are, a small one.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.18,1:21:29.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,写下来，詹姆斯·法兰西斯·瑞恩，爱阿华州\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Write this down: "James Francis Ryan? Iowa?"
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.22,1:21:33.02,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他吗，快看看\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"Do you know him?" Read the message! Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.69,1:21:39.46,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然认识他     知道他在哪里吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Yeah, of course I know him.   - Does he know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.53,1:21:46.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们偏离了降落区二十英里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah, we missed our dropzone by about 20 miles
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.00,1:21:50.19,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,降落的地方好像是布鲁维里什么的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and ended up way over by "Bumville" or some damn place.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.39,1:21:53.46,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他和其他人正要到这里集合\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Him, me and a couple of others were coming here to the rally point.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.67,1:21:59.31,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,却遇到一位上校正召集弟兄前往兰姆勒\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We ran into a colonel who was gathering up men to go to Ramelle.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.50,1:22:01.56,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,兰姆勒     去防守一座桥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Ramelle?   - To babysit a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.77,1:22:04.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最后一次看见他     好极了，谢谢你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- That's the last I've seen of him.   - Great! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.95,1:22:08.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,写谢谢，你看，谢谢     不客气\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Write "Thank you". Read. Thank you.   - You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.22,1:22:09.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大家过来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Assemble on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.96,1:22:13.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，中尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Thank you, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.56,1:22:18.52,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,兰姆勒\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Ramelle.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.52,1:22:24.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里，兰姆勒在麦德里特河畔\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We're here. There. Ramelle is on the Merderet River,right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.21,1:22:27.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的西南方\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Just to the southwest of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.47,1:22:29.76,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那座桥吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You know anything about that bridge we just talk about?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.97,1:22:34.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，瑟堡一直是盟军的目标\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah. The target has always been Cherbourg.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.58,1:22:39.70,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要占领深水港才能攻占巴黎，而隆美尔也知道\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We can't push on Paris until we take a deep water port and Rommel knows that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.91,1:22:44.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他会试着把装甲部队运过麦德里特河\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He's going to try to get his armour across the Merderet River anyway he can.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.62,1:22:49.46,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能在我们进攻瑟堡时夹击我们\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That way he can hit us in the flank when we make the turn for Cherbourg.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.66,1:22:55.40,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,所以有桥梁的村庄都成了重要的据点\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That makes any village on the river with a bridge solid gold real estate.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.71,1:23:17.04,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.62,1:23:28.19,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.41,1:24:09.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.48,1:24:12.44,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,废弃的雷达站\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}A radar site. It's got to be out of action.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.67,1:24:18.58,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,下面的沙坑里有敌人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Looks like we've got something in that sandbag bunker under the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.82,1:24:22.77,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,看到吗     对，我也这么想\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- See it?   - Yeah, that's my guess, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.01,1:24:27.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么     机枪，或许是MG-42\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What is it?   - Machine gun, probably MG-42.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.08,1:24:31.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人就是被它干掉的吗     也许瑞恩也在里面\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Is that what got those guys?   - Maybe one of them is Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.16,1:24:35.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不，他们是82队的，你的运气才没那么好\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}No, their patches are 82nd, so your luck's not that good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.33,1:24:40.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你们的脚程，但若我们悄悄地绕道\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I don't know how fast you are, but if we detour this way quick and quiet,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.27,1:24:41.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,德军就不会知道我们在这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}the Krauts will never even know we were here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.60,1:24:46.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,为何不绕道走\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What I'm trying to say is why don't we just go around the thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.18,1:24:50.90,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白，但不能够这样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I hear what you're saying, but we can't go around it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.38,1:24:56.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我支持莱宾的说法，避开那些机枪就行了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm with Reiben. I mean, we left those 88s.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.92,1:25:02.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,空军可不会专程来对付一挺机枪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}For the Air Force. They're not going to spend ordnance on one machine gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.92,1:25:04.18,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.46,1:25:10.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,绕路还是能达成任务，这并不是我们的任务，对吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We can skip it and still accomplish our mission. This isn't our mission, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.53,1:25:12.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利西，你想这样做吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Is that what you want to do, Mellish?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.93,1:25:15.40,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,任由其他部队中伏吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Leave it here so they can ambush another company?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.63,1:25:21.33,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我只是说这并非我们的目标\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}No, I'm simply saying it's seems an unnecessary risk given our objective.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.54,1:25:23.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目标是打胜仗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Our objective is to win the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.51,1:25:31.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我有不祥的预感\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It's just that I don't have a good feeling about this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.02,1:25:37.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候有过好的预感了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}When was the last time you felt good about anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.68,1:26:01.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，三个人冲前开火\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Alright. Three runners with suppressing fire.
