Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.86,1:28:30.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,山上安全了，干掉了四个     厄本\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Hill's clear. Four down and dead!   - Upham!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.93,1:28:34.52,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,收拾装备带上来，我们需要水和药物\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Grab the gear and get up here! We need water and extra dressing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.73,1:28:39.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,从药包里把吗啡拿出来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get the morphine out of the medical kit!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.11,1:28:53.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋     撒上磺胺粉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Son of a bitch!   - Get some sulfa on there.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.55,1:28:55.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的腿抬高     行了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Move my legs up.   - I got them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.89,1:28:57.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,快倒磺胺粉     听我说\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Pour sulfa.   - Listen to my voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.75,1:28:59.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你会没事的，医师\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You're going to be alright, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.59,1:29:03.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，很快就能上医疗船\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You're fine. You're going on a hospital ship.
