Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.94,1:29:14.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，把水壶给我     快\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Upham, give me your canteen!   - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.07,1:29:19.30,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会带你离开的     压着伤口\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- We're going to get you out of here.   - Put some pressure on it.
