Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.54,1:29:50.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德，子弹穿了出去，你背后有个弹孔\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Wade, you've got an exit wound. It's in the small of your back.
