Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.05,1:30:03.14,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,压住伤口\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Put some pressure on it. Put some pressure on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.35,1:30:05.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,压住伤口\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Put some pressure on it!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.36,1:30:08.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,用力一点\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Put some more pressure on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.59,1:30:12.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,还有更严重的伤口吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Is there anything bleeding worse than the others?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.93,1:30:16.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有，这里，知道在哪里吗，这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah, right here. Do you know what it is? Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.30,1:30:19.74,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你的手放到上面     我们正压着伤口\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I'll put your hand on it.   - We got some pressure on there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.97,1:30:21.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.01,1:30:26.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，那是我的肝脏\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Oh, my God! My liver! It's my liver!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.21,1:30:29.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,教我们该怎么救你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Tell us what to do. Tell us how to fix you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.71,1:30:32.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该怎么办，告诉我们\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What can we do? Tell us what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.38,1:30:38.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,给我一点吗啡\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I could use a little morphine.
