Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.23,1:30:45.16,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}OK. OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.30,1:30:50.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,什么     给他注射\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Sir? What?   - Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.34,1:30:54.43,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,给他注射\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.14,1:31:03.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死     韦德，我们正在注射\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I don't want to die!   - Here you go, Wade. Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.82,1:31:09.61,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,再注射一剂\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Give him another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.83,1:31:18.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mama...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.66,1:31:22.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.90,1:31:26.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I want to go home, I want go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.47,1:31:30.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mama, Mama, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.47,1:31:36.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mama, Mama, Mama, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.29,1:32:18.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾，抓住他\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Reiben, hold him!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.67,1:32:40.37,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.58,1:32:45.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,先叫他替韦德挖个坟墓\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}First make him mark and cover Wade's body for Grave Detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.18,1:32:50.31,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,也替那些伞兵挖个坟墓\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Same thing for the paratroopers down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.52,1:32:53.05,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,拿走他的装备，查问他\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Strip that stuff off him. Check him for intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.26,1:32:57.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,问这混蛋，韦德是不是他杀的，快问\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Ask this piece of shit if he shot Wade! Ask him!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.46,1:32:58.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有用吗     有\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Does it matter?   - It does!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.57,1:33:05.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,闭上你的臭嘴\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Shut up with that filthy pig Latin.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.24,1:33:10.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克森，你中弹了吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Jackson, are you hit?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.21,1:33:14.47,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦伤而已\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It just skinned the arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.68,1:33:20.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,把伤口处理好，你和中士留意周围\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get it cleaned and dressed. You and Sarge watch the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.22,1:33:26.31,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他求我们别杀他     厄本，我不管他说什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- He says, "Please don't shoot."   - I don't care what he says, Upham.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.62,1:33:30.52,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，你要让他们杀他吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sir? Sir, are you going to let them kill him?
