Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.75,1:35:35.65,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢美国人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I like American.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.03,1:35:45.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,轮船威里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Steamboat Willie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.76,1:35:50.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,轮船威里     轮船威里，美国人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Steamboat Willie.   - Steamboat Willie. American.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.41,1:36:07.28,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他还没完成     那是你的想法，来吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- He says he's not finished.   - That's what you think. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.32,1:36:19.12,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，我喜欢美国人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Please! I like America!
