Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.74,1:36:32.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,贝蒂小姐，好性感\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Betty Boop! What a dish.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.91,1:36:34.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,贝蒂嘉宝，腿很美\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Betty Grable. Nice gams.
