Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.05,1:36:47.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你看到吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I say can you see
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.19,1:36:50.28,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我说\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I say...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.20,1:36:58.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的希特勒\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fuck Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.87,1:37:02.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的希特勒\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fuck Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.65,1:37:15.81,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，他说他替韦德的死难过\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sir, he says he's sorry about Wade. He says he's sorry about Wade.
