Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.74,1:37:45.61,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,朝那方向走一千步，然后脱掉蒙眼布\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}to march 1,000 paces in that direction.Then he can take off the blindfold.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.82,1:37:48.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,向首个遇到的盟军自首\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He turns himself in to the first Allied patrol.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.68,1:37:50.28,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说笑吗，放他走\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Are you kidding? We're letting him go?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.49,1:37:54.18,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾，他是战俘，不能带着他走\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He's a POW, Reiben. We can't take him with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.39,1:37:58.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我军自会处置他     算他命大\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Our guys will pick him up.   - That was a close shave.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.20,1:38:01.16,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,真幸运\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Lucky Strikes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.03,1:38:07.20,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,带我去看球赛\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Take me out to the ball game...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.40,1:38:13.10,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,万一他被敌军救回，又会回来作战的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Only if he doesn't get picked up by his own and get thrown back into circulation.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.64,1:38:18.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，你白白放过了敌人     简直白痴\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Captain, you just let the enemy go.   - This is such bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.78,1:38:22.58,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没错     白痴，这是白痴吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- You all got that right.   - Bullshit? This is bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.79,1:38:25.35,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,难道可以射杀战俘吗，这样是有违军法的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Shooting a prisoner is OK? It's against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.55,1:38:29.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,军法跟你的新朋友一起走了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The goddam rules just walked off with your new friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.46,1:38:34.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，这样做是对的吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}But I guess that was the decent thing to do, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.47,1:38:44.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,收拾东西，出发吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get your gear. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.34,1:38:49.61,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你们听到了，收拾东西\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You heard him. Gear up.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.68,1:38:53.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉刚下了命令     是的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- The Captain just gave you an order.   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.15,1:38:57.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他下令攻下机枪台一样，真是大英雄\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Like the one he gave to take this machine gun. That was a real doozy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.09,1:38:59.52,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你太过分了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You're out of line!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.76,1:39:02.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他命令我们拿下这里真是英明\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That was one hell of a call coming to take this nest,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.89,1:39:05.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们却因此丧失了一位队友\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}but what the hell, we only lost one of our guys going for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.03,1:39:09.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩妈妈一定很高兴，知道她儿子的性命\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I hope Mama Ryan's really happy knowing that little Jimmy's life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.50,1:39:11.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,比我们两位队友的还重要\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}was more important than two of our guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.07,1:39:15.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们还没找到他吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}But then, we haven't found them, have we?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.84,1:39:18.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你     放开我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Hey...   - Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.47,1:39:20.84,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾，起来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Reiben, get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.11,1:39:25.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,拿起东西，入列\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Gear up. Fall in.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.19,1:39:32.62,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我要退出这项任务\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm done with this mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.49,1:39:39.98,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.86,1:39:42.85,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,长官     你不能一走了之\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Sir...   - Don't you walk away from your captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.10,1:39:45.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾，给我回来     不\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Reiben, get back in line!   - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.50,1:39:48.20,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁可坐牢也不想继续了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'll spend the rest of my life in the stockade rather than go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.40,1:39:50.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我说最后一遍     上尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I'm not going to ask you again.   - Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.01,1:39:53.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴     入列\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- This is bullshit!   - Fall in!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.61,1:39:56.84,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你要因为瑞恩而杀我吗     不，是因为我讨厌你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Are you going to shoot me over Ryan?   - No, because I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.05,1:39:59.24,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他想走就让他走吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}If he wants to go, just let him go!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.45,1:40:02.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你不管吗，上尉，你看到了吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Are you letting this happen? Captain! You see this?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.89,1:40:05.82,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，瑞恩已经死了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain. Sir, Ryan's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.06,1:40:08.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴     这里情况不妙\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Bullshit!   - We have a situation here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.62,1:40:11.02,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我有很强的第六感\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I have a sixth sense. I know it in my bones.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.23,1:40:13.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你不杀德军却要杀我吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We didn't kill the Kraut. Now you're going to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.10,1:40:16.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他比你好     下手吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- He's better than you.   - Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.60,1:40:21.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,打我的腿     我要打你的大嘴巴\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Put one in my leg...   - I'll shoot you in your big mouth!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.20,1:40:22.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说，开枪吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Put your money where your mouth is and do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.07,1:40:25.70,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你总是那么多话说\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You don't know how to shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.91,1:40:30.50,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，求求你     赌金有多少了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Captain, please!   - What's the pool on me up to?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.71,1:40:34.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个懦弱的混蛋     中士，我在等你开枪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- You are a coward son of a bitch!   - I'm waiting, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.22,1:40:37.28,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,赌金累积到有多少了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What's the pool on me up to right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.49,1:40:39.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有多少了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What's it up to?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.99,1:40:42.82,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,三百块吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What is it? 300 dollars, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.03,1:40:45.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个老师\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm a schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.83,1:40:52.10,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我教英文作文\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I teach English Composition...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.30,1:40:54.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,在宾夕法尼亚州一个叫艾德里的小镇\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}in this little town called Addley, Pennsylvania.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.87,1:41:00.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这十一年来我在汤玛斯爱迪生高校任教\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}In the last 11 years, I've been at Thomas Alva Edison High School.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.14,1:41:06.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,在春季我是棒球教练\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I was the coach of the baseball team in the springtime.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.52,1:41:10.25,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我真该死\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'll be doggone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.45,1:41:13.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我在家乡告诉人家我的职业时\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Back home, when I tell people what I do for a living
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.12,1:41:17.79,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他们觉得“一看就知道”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}they think, "Well, that figures."
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.86,1:41:22.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但到了这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}But over here, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.80,1:41:27.10,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,却成为了一个大秘密\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}a big, big mystery.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.37,1:41:32.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我变了一点\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}So, I guess I've changed some.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.64,1:41:36.81,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有时我想我改变了很多\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sometimes I wonder if I've changed so much
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.01,1:41:41.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,回家后也许妻子会不认得我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}my wife is even going to recognise me whenever I get back to her...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.99,1:41:45.85,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我不能向她\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and how I'll ever be able to...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.09,1:41:50.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,诉说像今天这种事情\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}tell her about days like today.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.30,1:41:56.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Ryan...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.60,1:42:00.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我对瑞恩一无所知，我才不管\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I don't know anything about Ryan. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.34,1:42:02.30,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我毫无关系，那只是个名字\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He means nothing to me, it's just a name,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.54,1:42:09.74,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但要是到兰姆勒带他回家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}but if going to Ramelle and finding him so he can go home,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.95,1:42:13.75,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,能让我回到妻子身边\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}if that earns me the right to get back to my wife, then...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.95,1:42:16.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我会接下这项任务\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}...then that's my mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.09,1:42:23.49,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你想退出，重返战场吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You want to leave? You want to go off and fight the war?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.73,1:42:28.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.56,1:42:35.49,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会阻止你，我甚至会替你申请\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Alright, I won't stop you. I'll even put in the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.74,1:42:40.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道我多杀一人便离家越远\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I just know that with every man I kill, the farther away from home I feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.29,1:44:10.23,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 昔日的回忆涌现 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}by memories of days gone by
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.13,1:44:17.00,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 孤独中你嘲弄我 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}In my solitude you taunt me
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.21,1:44:21.97,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 勾起不死的记忆 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}with memories that never die
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.18,1:44:27.01,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 我坐在椅上满怀绝望 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I sit in my chair filled with despair
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.22,1:44:32.18,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 比任何人都要哀伤 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}There's no one could be so sad
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.42,1:44:36.82,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 看着坐着的地方尽是阴霾 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}With gloom everywhere I sit and I stare
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.03,1:44:41.52,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 我很快就会疯掉 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I know that I'll soon go mad
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.74,1:44:52.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有坦克，躲好\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Half-track! Cover!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.59,1:45:12.49,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁开枪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Who's doing the shooting? Who's doing the shooting?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.98,1:45:35.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,准备行动，攻击左边\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get ready to move. Take their left flank!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.65,1:45:37.85,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点，以防有余兵\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hold on and make sure they're down.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.37,1:46:02.50,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是101师，现在出来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}101st! We're coming out!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.48,1:46:12.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,装甲兵第二师\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That was a recon. element, 2nd SS.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.82,1:46:17.28,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在等待情报，一定是他们了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We've been expecting a probe. That must have been it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.19,1:46:22.49,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,第二突击队C连米勒上尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain Miller, Charlie Company, 2nd Rangers.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.70,1:46:24.79,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,501师E连汉德森下士\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Corporal Henderson, Easy Company, 501st.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.00,1:46:28.83,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,506团第一队瑞恩     506团第三队托恩比\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Ryan, First of 506th.   - Toynbee, Third of 506th.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.04,1:46:34.77,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·法兰西斯·瑞恩     对，你怎么会知道\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- James Francis Ryan?   - Yes,sir.How did you guess that?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.55,1:46:51.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,看来敌方攻势猛烈     对，是小组部队的进攻\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Looks like you got hit pretty hard.   - Yes,sir.Small unit action.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.26,1:46:58.63,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的88毫米炮威力强劲\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}They came in and beat the hell out of us with 88s.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.14,1:47:07.54,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你们就是救兵，我可要投诉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Tell you what. If you're our relief, I'm going to file a complaint.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.78,1:47:10.20,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会怪你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I wouldn't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.44,1:47:13.64,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你的指挥官\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Who's your CO?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.85,1:47:16.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,原本是简宁斯上尉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It would've been Captain Jennings.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.69,1:47:19.80,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但下士已是这儿的最高级军官了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm afraid the best we can muster up now is a corporal.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.25,1:47:24.23,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那你们为什么来这里\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}So what are you guys all about?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.46,1:47:27.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为他而来，瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We're here for him. Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.20,1:47:30.03,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.97,1:47:42.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你是爱阿华州的詹姆斯·法兰西斯·瑞恩吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}James Francis Ryan of lowa?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.41,1:47:47.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,对，爱阿华州佩顿市，这是怎么回事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yes, sir. Peyton,Iowa, that's correct. What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.58,1:47:52.28,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你兄长阵亡了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Your brothers were killed in combat.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.25,1:48:01.20,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Which ones?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.77,1:48:06.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,全部\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.08,1:48:16.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}On the level?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.05,1:48:21.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是真的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah, I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.68,1:48:24.62,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大概要一段时间才能接受\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You might want to take some time with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.85,1:48:28.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你想到什么地方\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}If there's someplace you want to go and...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.89,1:48:39.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事     瑞恩的兄弟去世了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What's this all about?   - Ryan lost his brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.94,1:48:42.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个     全部\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Which one?   - All of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.28,1:48:53.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你们专程跑来告诉我吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You came all the way out here to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.35,1:48:59.58,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你要回家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You're going home.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.79,1:49:02.52,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们奉命带你回去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Our orders are to bring you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.02,1:49:08.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,带我回去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Bring me back?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.80,1:49:14.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,下士，我不是想令你人手短缺，但这是命令\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Corporal,I don't mean to leave you more short-handed,but orders are orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.79,1:49:17.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,想跟什么人联络吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Any communications about when you will be relieved?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.63,1:49:20.57,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不知道南方的情况\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We can't tell. We don't know what's happening south of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.81,1:49:24.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的命令不许我擅离职守\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}My orders don't include me abandoning my post.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.34,1:49:26.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，但情况有变\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I understand that, but this changes things.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.18,1:49:29.45,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认同\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I don't see that it does, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.09,1:49:34.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这是美军参谋长的命令\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The Chief of Staff for the US Army says it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.88,1:49:37.09,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们奉命死守这座桥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Our orders are to hold this bridge at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.29,1:49:40.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我方战机已经把麦德里特河的所有桥梁炸断\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Our planes in the 82nd have taken out every bridge across the Merderet,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.60,1:49:43.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,除了瓦隆尼和这里两处\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}with the exception of two: one at Valognes and this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.59,1:49:46.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要是给德军拿下我们就要退守\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}If the Germans take it, we'll have to displace.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.33,1:49:51.23,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,部队的任务是一回事，但你要离开了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Private.It's one thing that your outfit wants to stay,but your party's over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.46,1:49:53.33,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,援军到达前我不能离开\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I can't leave before the reinforcements are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.53,1:49:55.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,三分钟内收拾行装\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You've got three minutes to get your gear.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.13,1:49:59.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那他们怎么办     混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What about them,there's barely...   - Hey,asshole!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.08,1:50:03.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们两位队友已经为你送命\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Two of our guys already died trying to find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.49,1:50:12.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗     是的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Sir?   - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.99,1:50:26.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫什么名字     艾文·韦德和艾德林·卡帕佐\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What were their names?   - Irwin Wade and Adrian Caparzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.51,1:50:30.02,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德和谁\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Wade and?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.34,1:50:33.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,卡帕佐\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Caparzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.38,1:50:47.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没有理由要这样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.86,1:50:54.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这样没道理，我有什么资格离开\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It doesn't make any sense, sir. Why do I deserve to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.20,1:50:57.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是他们，他们也同样努力\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Why not any of these guys? They all fought just as hard as me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.03,1:51:05.14,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你死后传讯员就要跟\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Is that what they're supposed to tell your mother
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.35,1:51:08.40,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲这样说吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}when they send her another folded American flag?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.66,1:51:18.91,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她说你在这里找到我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Tell her that when you found me I was here,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.12,1:51:21.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟军中其他兄弟在一起\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and I was with the only brothers that I have left,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.09,1:51:26.18,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎样也不会离弃他们\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and that there was no way I was going to desert them.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.39,1:51:31.56,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,她应该会明白，我不会离开这座桥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I think she'll understand that. There's no way I'm leaving this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.61,1:52:16.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么办\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What are your orders?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.48,1:52:22.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,中士，我们进入了一个奇异的国度\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sergeant, we have crossed some strange boundary here.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.72,1:52:25.24,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都异乎寻常\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Our world has taken a turn for the surreal.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.48,1:52:28.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但问题始终要解决\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Clearly, but the question still stands.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.09,1:52:32.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，你觉得怎样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I don't know. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.16,1:52:35.65,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会想知道\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You don't want to know what I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.73,1:52:39.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我想知道\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}No, Mike, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.07,1:52:46.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我一方面同意他的说法他有什么资格\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Part of me thinks the kid's right. What's he done to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.17,1:52:51.18,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他既然想留下来，我们就干脆回去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}If he wants to stay here, fine. Let's leave him and go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.18,1:52:54.04,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.25,1:52:59.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但我还有一个想法，要是我们也留下来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}But another part of me thinks, "What if by some miracle we stay"
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.58,1:53:02.35,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,会缔造什么奇迹呢\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"and actually make it out of here?"
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.55,1:53:06.46,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有天我们回想此事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Some day we might look back on this and decide that
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.69,1:53:11.15,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,也许会觉得在这场混帐战争中\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}saving Private Ryan was the one decent thing we pulled out of
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.40,1:53:16.16,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救瑞恩是唯一的好事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}this whole godawful, shitty mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.37,1:53:23.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的想法，上尉，如你所言\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That's what I was thinking, sir. Like you said, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.68,1:53:29.84,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会留下来一起为团聚战斗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We do that, we all earn the right to go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.65,1:53:34.78,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Oh, brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.42,1:53:40.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些武器\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This is everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.56,1:53:46.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,23毫米机枪、17枚手榴弹、11个霍金斯地雷\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You've got the.230 calibre machine guns, 17 grenades, 11 Hawkins mines.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.90,1:53:50.10,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你有两支火箭筒，但只能发射八次\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You've got two bazookas, but they've only got eight rounds left.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.30,1:53:52.43,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,还有各式小手枪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}And assorted small arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.64,1:53:55.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,本来有60毫米迫击炮，但已损毁\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We had a.60 mortar, but an arty round took it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.07,1:53:58.70,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军坦克压过来我们吐口水攻击好了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Might as well be spit wads if they roll on us with tanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.91,1:54:03.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军当然会动用坦克     你有什么意见\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Which they're sure to do.   - What are you thinking, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.72,1:54:07.12,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我提议进行夹击\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm thinking I'm going to whip around the flanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.46,1:54:14.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要把他们引到大街\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Unless we can draw them up the main road between the buildings,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.93,1:54:18.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,用瓦砾造一个瓶颈\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}where all the rubble makes a bit of a bottleneck
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.66,1:54:20.82,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,让坦克无用武之地吗     可以的话\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Disable him?   - If we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.03,1:54:24.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,造个六十吨的路障，然后展开夹击\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Make a 60-tonne roadblock. Then we've got a fighting chance at her flanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.87,1:54:27.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,好，分散他们，别让他们集结\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Good. Split them up, don't let them mass.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.21,1:54:30.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,然后逐一击破，再退回大桥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hit them hard one-on-one, and fall back to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.28,1:54:34.61,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,下面放一台机枪，另一台置于高处\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Machine gun on the move down here, number two up high to piss on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.81,1:54:39.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,计划就是这样，杰克森\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That would be the idea. Jackson!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.52,1:54:41.82,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话我想你去钟楼\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}If we can, I'd like to get you up in that bell tower.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.02,1:54:45.05,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,知道     我会给你安排帮手\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Yes, sir.   - I'll give you some company.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.29,1:54:51.20,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,也好，还要30毫米狙击枪和一千发子弹\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Some company couldn't hurt. A.30 with about a 1,000 rounds would be OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.43,1:54:53.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,帕克，有工作给你\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Parker, job opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.60,1:54:55.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It's not the worst idea ever,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.57,1:54:59.23,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但胜负关键在于把坦克弄到街上让我们夹击\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}but everything depends on getting the tank down the road for us to knock out.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.44,1:55:02.77,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么计划\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}How the hell do you plan on doing that?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.97,1:55:05.64,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他说得对，空降师的队友刚说\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He's right. As our colleague from Airborne pointed out
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.84,1:55:08.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有的是口水\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}what we've got is a bunch of spit wads.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.31,1:55:12.15,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但把坦克引来后怎么应付\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}How do we stop the tank if we get it to commit?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.35,1:55:13.82,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,先用兔子引它追赶\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Give it a rabbit to chase.
