Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.22,1:55:53.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,用一只军袜装满炸药\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You take a standard GI sock, cram it full with Composition B,
