Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.60,1:56:05.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有粘力，所以叫粘附式炸弹\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It's a bomb that sticks. It's a sticky bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.30,1:56:09.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有更好的方法，尽管说出来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Come up with a better way to knock the tracks off a tank, I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.44,1:56:12.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错，我们要把袜子奉献\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This is good. Now we have to surrender our socks!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.46,1:56:29.05,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,拉上去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Haul away.
