Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.88,1:58:02.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要是退到这里，最后一个活人负责炸桥\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}They push us this far, the last man alive blows the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.42,1:58:05.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,导火线能烧三十秒，告诉大家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We've only got a 30-second delay on the fuse, so tell everyone
