Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.47,1:58:50.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从英国出发时也会分发香烟\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}When we shipped out of England we got cigarettes
