Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.45,1:59:08.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这差事混帐得不得了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Yeah. "Fucked-Up Beyond All Recognition", right?
