Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.81,1:59:34.44,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“苦差”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"FUBAR."
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.32,2:00:15.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的歌声\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Who's that singing, sir?
