Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.06,2:00:22.32,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,她为什么这么伤心\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What is she so upset about?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.53,2:00:27.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,情人离异，但她的面容历历在目\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Her lover left her, but she still sees his face everywhere she goes.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.93,2:00:30.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That would do it.
