Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.77,2:01:12.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么，她曾经唱过     是副歌\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- What was that? She sang it before.   - The chorus.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.41,2:01:14.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,副歌\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The chorus.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.31,2:01:17.21,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 每当你耳语喃喃 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"And you speak softly in my ear."
