Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.66,2:01:36.90,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说，你使我莫名的兴奋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}...to be honest, I find myself curiously aroused by you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.10,2:01:38.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,棒极了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Marvellous.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.84,2:01:42.57,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌很哀伤，开始时她唱着\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}It's a really melancholy song. At the beginning of the song she says:
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.77,2:01:48.58,歌曲,,0000,0000,0000,,∮ 你离去后，我就伤心绝望 ∮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"And then one day you left me and I've been desperate ever since."
