Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.98,2:01:55.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,再听多几首这种歌不用德军开枪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Any more songs like this, the Krauts won't have to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.62,2:01:58.25,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我就割脉自杀了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm just going to slit my own wrists.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.46,2:02:00.89,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，你好奇怪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You're a strange bird, Upham.
