Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.63,2:03:52.47,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不起哥哥的样貌\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I can't see my brothers' faces.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.67,2:03:57.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样努力也想不起来，你试过这样吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I've been trying and I can't see their faces at all. Has that happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.71,2:04:00.14,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你要想想发生过的事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You've got to think of a context.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.25,2:04:04.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.52,2:04:08.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不能只想他们的样子，要想些具体事情\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You don't just think about their faces, you think about something specific,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.42,2:04:10.75,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的共同经历\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}something you've done together.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.46,2:04:17.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我想家的时候想得很具体\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}When I want to think of home, I think of something specific.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.46,2:04:21.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起后院的吊床\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I think of my hammock in the backyard
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.47,2:04:26.84,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是妻子戴起我的旧手套修剪玫瑰花丛\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}or my wife pruning the rose bushes in a pair of my old work gloves.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.14,2:04:35.60,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有一晚两个哥哥把我弄醒\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This one night, two of my brothers woke me up in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.35,2:04:40.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,说要给我惊喜\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}They said they had a surprise for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.89,2:04:44.05,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,他们带我到谷仓的阁楼\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}They took me to the barn up into the loft
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.26,2:04:48.16,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,原来大哥丹尼\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and there was my oldest brother Dan
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.39,2:04:51.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,跟爱莉丝·贾汀在里面\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}with Alice Jardine!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.97,2:04:58.43,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,想像一下，那女孩从树上掉下来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Picture a girl who just took a nosedive from the ugly tree
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.67,2:05:01.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,会让所有树枝都给压断\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and hit every branch coming down!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.17,2:05:05.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼脱去她的衬衫\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}And Dan's got her shirt off...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.98,2:05:12.68,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,接着要把胸罩也脱下时肖恩突然大叫\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}So he's trying to get her bra off and all of a sudden Sean screams out
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.88,2:05:16.84,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“丹尼，你年纪还小，不可以这样”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"Danny, you're a young man. Don't do it!"
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.59,2:05:22.08,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉丝·贾汀马上大叫，跳了起来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Alice Jardine hears this and she screams and jumps up
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.33,2:05:25.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,想冲出去，但她的头给衬衫蒙着\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and tries to run out, but she's got her shirt over her head.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.93,2:05:29.76,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,所以撞到墙壁，晕了过去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}She runs into the wall and knocks herself out.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.97,2:05:33.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼很生气，追着我们\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Now Dan is so mad at us. He starts coming after us,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:34.07,2:05:38.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,但爱莉丝晕倒了，他要弄醒她\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}but at the same time Alice is unconscious. He's got to wake her up.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.61,2:05:41.31,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,于是一手抓着她的腿猛拉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He grabs her by a leg and drags her
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.51,2:05:44.85,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,一手拿着铲子追赶肖恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and at the same time he picks up a shovel and goes after Sean!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.05,2:05:49.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,肖恩说“你干嘛打我，我是在帮你”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}And Sean says, "Why are you trying to hit me? I just did you a favour!"
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.89,2:05:54.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼更加生气，乱挥铲子\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}This makes Dan more angry. He tries to swing this thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:54.93,2:05:58.62,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,最后铲子脱手，打破了火油灯\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He loses his shovel. It goes out of his grasp and hits a kerosene lantern.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.83,2:06:04.43,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸着火，谷仓几乎给烧掉\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The thing explodes. The whole barn almost goes up because of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.52,2:06:21.85,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是最后一晚，丹第二天就上战场去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That was it, that was the last... Dan went off to Basic the next day.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.05,2:06:25.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这是四兄弟最后一次共聚\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That was the last night the four of us were together.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.92,2:06:27.95,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了两年\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}That was two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.06,2:06:32.12,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.23,2:06:37.93,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,再说说妻子和玫瑰花丛的事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Tell me about your wife and those rose bushes.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.14,2:06:43.04,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那些事要留给自己\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}No. No, that one I save just for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:48.61,2:07:50.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人从东面开来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Enemy from the east.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.94,2:07:56.50,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,两台虎式坦克，两辆装甲车\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}He sees two Tiger tanks, two Panzer tanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.75,2:08:00.65,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,五十人以上的步兵队伍\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Infantry. 50 plus change.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.53,2:08:12.52,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,分散，各就各位，莱宾，去当兔子\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Disperse! You know what to do. Reiben, get on the rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:12.76,2:08:17.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，躲起来     梅利西、汉德森，准备开火\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Upham, get some cover.   - Mellish and Henderson, lock and load!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.20,2:08:19.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,大家检查武器\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Everybody check your ammo!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.94,2:08:24.60,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾，祝你好运     不用祝福，我生来幸运\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Good luck,Reiben!   - I don't need any luck,I was born lucky!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.66,2:08:40.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着五枚曳光弹     知道，照亮两端\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- One in five tracer.   - Yes, and tracers point both ways.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.19,2:08:44.46,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去检查顶端的空间\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Why don't you check the head space and she should run.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.87,2:08:55.74,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，快点\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham, hustle up!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.49,2:09:49.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本下士，这里没有30毫米口径机枪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Corporal Upham. We don't have a.30 calibre machine gun here.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.59,2:09:55.05,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利西和钟楼的杰克森才需要这个\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Either Mister Mellish or Mr Jackson in the bell tower needs that.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.30,2:09:58.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，杰克森有子弹，去拿给梅利西\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham! Jackson's fine, turn around to Mellish!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.89,2:10:23.62,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多步兵，不知道会否上钓\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}There's a ton of infantry. I don't know if they took the bait, though.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.75,2:10:50.02,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,还有口香糖吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Have you got any more of that?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.83,2:11:38.06,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,装甲车没有上当\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The Panzers didn't take the bait.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.11,2:11:45.84,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,步兵团正向左进发\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}The infantry's moving to the left.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:46.04,2:11:49.21,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,一辆装甲车跟二十人刚刚开过\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}A half-track just went by with about 20 troops.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:28.21,2:13:31.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利西、汉德森，移位\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mellish, Henderson! Displace!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:53.00,2:13:56.90,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,点火\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Do it, now! Light it up! You! Light it!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:08.22,2:14:12.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,右边有三十人，设法阻截他们\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}30 infantry on the right flank. Get over there, find a hole and stop them!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:12.79,2:14:15.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,移位\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Displace!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.10,2:14:27.87,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:42.64,2:14:45.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,目标清除     去吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Clear! OK,   - Go!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:45.82,2:14:47.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Krauts!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.16,2:14:51.39,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,向右边进攻\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Right flank!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:27.06,2:15:29.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,伏下\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Get down, get down!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.34,2:15:39.46,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，30毫米口径子弹\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham! Thirty cal, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.67,2:15:42.90,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉上尉左翼快失守\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Find the Captain, this flank's going to fold!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:37.89,2:16:40.29,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,车子还在动\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Traversing! He's still in this fight!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:41.80,2:16:44.37,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩，伏下\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}No! Ryan, get down, get down!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:57.24,2:16:59.47,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Ryan!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:17.73,2:17:19.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞恩\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Ryan!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:20.83,2:17:23.14,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴     放开我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Keep your mouth.   - Shut Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.35,2:17:25.07,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧     放开我\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Are you alright?   - Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:25.27,2:17:27.74,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，我也没事，谢谢\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm fine too, Captain. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.97,2:17:32.44,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,夹击他们，扔手榴弹过去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hit them from both sides. Get aboard! Get a grenade in there!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:36.48,2:17:37.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,手榴弹\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Grenade!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.69,2:17:42.62,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是20毫米口径机枪\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}20 mill! 20 mill!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:42.82,2:17:44.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是重型机枪，干掉它\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Flak gun, 20 mm. Take it out!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:57.94,2:18:01.34,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,机枪给覆盖着，打不到\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Heavy weapon in defilade below! I ain't got a shot!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:05.88,2:18:10.22,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,钳子队形，帕克，目标在八点钟方向\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Pincer move! Parker! Targets eight o'clock, low!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:10.43,2:18:12.51,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,愿天主赐我力量\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}God grant me strength.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:25.97,2:18:29.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，快移位\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Let's go, displace! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:45.52,2:18:48.72,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，躲好\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Cover! Upham, cover!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:04.94,2:19:07.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,30毫米子弹用光了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm out of.30 calibre.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:10.44,2:19:12.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天主赐我力量，教我的手打仗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Blessed be the Lord my strength, which teaches my hands to war
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.21,2:19:15.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,教我的指头作战\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}and my fingers to fight.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:24.16,2:19:28.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,天主是我的堡垒、我的高塔和解脱者\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}My goodness and my fortress. My high tower and deliverer.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:32.00,2:19:34.73,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我的盾牌、我的依靠\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}My shield and He in whom I trust.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:38.31,2:19:40.33,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，宝贝\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Here you go, baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.93,2:20:05.16,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,帕克，伏下\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Parker, get down!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.32,2:20:28.62,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，那20毫米口径手枪真要命\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain, that 20 mm is killing us.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.82,2:20:33.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要毁掉它     我到上面去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- We've got to try to flank it somehow.   - Let me get over there for a top shot.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.62,2:21:00.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:18.84,2:21:23.71,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本，拿子弹来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham, Upham! Upham, ammo, goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:06.82,2:22:10.65,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,卡住了，拿30毫米子弹给我     用光了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I'm jammed! Got any.30 calibre?   - I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:22.74,2:22:25.17,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham. Upham!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:17.86,2:23:19.42,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Reiben!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:22.96,2:23:24.16,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Reiben!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:51.32,2:23:55.66,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,用光了，有人有子弹吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm out! I need another bandolier. Anybody got a bandolier?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:26.86,2:24:28.92,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:13.47,2:25:18.57,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，听我说，别这样\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Let's stop, let's stop! Listen to me! Stop! No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,2:25:45.37,2:25:47.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:54.98,2:25:59.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Son of a bitch, son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:59.72,2:26:01.81,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:23.20,2:27:27.61,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,用光了，那些60毫米炮弹\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I'm out! Those.60 rounds...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:27.81,2:27:30.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,没有炮管也可以用     怎样用\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- We can use them without the tube.   - How?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:30.88,2:27:34.14,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,这是引爆线，扔出去就行了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Fuse-arming wire, set back and heave it!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:49.46,2:27:51.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Panzer schreck!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:08.98,2:28:10.97,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:25.43,2:28:27.96,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,到最后防线去\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}We're going to the Alamo.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:37.84,2:28:40.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,最后防线\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Alamo! Alamo!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:59.33,2:29:02.82,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们，你们撤退     你跟着来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- We'll take it. You fall back!   - You be right behind us!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:03.07,2:29:05.00,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很快回来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}As soon as we're in business.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:09.11,2:29:11.54,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,莱宾，移位\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Displace. Reiben!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:13.81,2:29:15.84,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,装弹\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Reload!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:04.03,2:30:05.50,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,开炮\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Alright, go!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:06.67,2:30:09.57,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,要炸桥了，快逃     快离开\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- We're blowing the bridge! Get off!   - Off the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:33.66,2:30:36.53,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,中士，麦克，你没事吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Sarge! Mike, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:36.73,2:30:39.13,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我被风吹倒了     走吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- I just got the wind knocked out of me.   - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:39.33,2:30:42.23,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,躲好，要炸桥了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Take cover, we're going to blow this bridge!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:44.17,2:30:45.90,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:50.61,2:30:52.94,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,虎式坦克要过桥了\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Tiger company's coming across the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:25.68,2:31:28.88,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，找个地方躲好\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain, get behind something!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:54.71,2:31:56.47,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mike!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:01.25,2:32:03.01,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Mike!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:45.49,2:32:49.55,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，你去哪里，回来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Captain, where the hell are you going? Captain, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:42.68,2:34:44.11,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,厄本\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Upham!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:13.77,2:35:15.90,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:01.29,2:36:03.26,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,救护员\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:05.86,2:36:08.52,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,有救护员吗\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Medic! We've got a medic?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:15.17,2:36:18.86,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,是P-51反坦克轰炸机\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}They're tankbusters, sir. P-51s.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:19.07,2:36:21.16,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的守护天使\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Angels on our shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:27.18,2:36:29.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}What, sir?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:33.32,2:36:35.38,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}James...
Dialogue: 0,2:36:36.62,2:36:38.75,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别辜负\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Earn this.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:42.33,2:36:44.69,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,别辜负大家\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Earn it.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:13.10,2:37:15.85,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“亲爱的瑞恩太太”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"My dear Mrs Ryan."
Dialogue: 0,2:37:16.50,2:37:20.56,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“我有个喜讯要带给你”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"It's with a profound sense of joy that I write to inform you"
Dialogue: 0,2:37:20.67,2:37:25.41,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“就是令郞二等兵詹姆斯·瑞恩安然无恙”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"that your son, Private James Ryan, is well"
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.51,2:37:29.89,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“现在正从欧洲的战线回国”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"and at this moment on his way home from European battlefields."
Dialogue: 0,2:37:30.28,2:37:34.44,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“詹姆斯尽忠职守”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"Reports indicate that James did his duty in combat"
Dialogue: 0,2:37:34.60,2:37:37.54,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“勇气过人、坚毅不屈”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"with great courage and steadfast dedication"
Dialogue: 0,2:37:37.85,2:37:42.41,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“纵使他得知兄弟阵亡”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"even after he was informed of the loss your family has suffered"
Dialogue: 0,2:37:42.64,2:37:47.28,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“仍坚持参与这场铲除独裁暴政的伟大战争”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"in this great campaign to rid the world of tyranny and oppression."
Dialogue: 0,2:37:47.69,2:37:50.79,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“我与战争部长”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"I take great pleasure injoining the Secretary of War"
Dialogue: 0,2:37:50.99,2:37:55.80,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“美军同仁及美国国民”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"the men and women of the US Army, and the citizens of a grateful nation"
Dialogue: 0,2:37:55.86,2:38:01.75,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“仅此祝你身体健康，与詹姆斯一起活得愉快”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"in wishing you good health and many years of happiness with James."
Dialogue: 0,2:38:02.31,2:38:06.77,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“虽然爱子平安归国”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"Nothing, not even the safe return of a beloved son"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:07.11,2:38:11.14,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“也无法弥补你和千千万万个美国家庭”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"can compensate you or the thousands of other American families"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:11.36,2:38:14.43,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“在战争中遭受的创痛”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"who have suffered great loss in this tragic war."
Dialogue: 0,2:38:14.75,2:38:16.87,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“我想与你分享”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"I might share with you some words"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:16.97,2:38:22.32,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“一番在悲痛绝望中支持着我的说话”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"which have sustained me through nights of peril, loss and heartache"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:22.73,2:38:26.99,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“是这样的一番说话”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"and I quote, 'I pray that our heavenly Father"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:27.07,2:38:30.10,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“愿天主安抚你的丧子之痛”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"may assuage the anguish of your bereavement"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:30.38,2:38:34.24,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“让你永远怀念远去的挚爱”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"and leave you only the cherished memory of the loved and lost"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:34.47,2:38:36.71,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“神圣的荣耀都归于你们”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"and the solemn pride that must be yours"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:36.91,2:38:42.18,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“因你们为自由付出了重大的代价”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"to have laid a so costly a sacrifice upon the altar of freedom."
Dialogue: 0,2:38:42.45,2:38:44.35,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“林肯敬上”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"Abraham Lincoln."
Dialogue: 0,2:38:44.66,2:38:47.05,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“深表敬意”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"Yours very sincerely and respectfully"
Dialogue: 0,2:38:47.29,2:38:50.92,画外音,,0000,0000,0000,,“参谋长马歇尔上将”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&\fsp0\fscy100%}"George C. Marshall. General, Chief of Staff."
Dialogue: 0,2:39:41.83,2:39:47.28,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我家人也来了，他们想跟我来\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}My family is with me today. They wanted to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:49.96,2:39:55.12,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,说真的，我不知道到这里来会有什么感受\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}To be honest with you, I wasn't sure how I would feel coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:57.53,2:40:03.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都想着当日你在桥上说的话\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Every day, I think about what you said to me that day on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:05.13,2:40:09.33,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我努力活好每一天\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I've tried to live my life the best I could.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:09.63,2:40:12.36,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,希望这已经足够\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I hope that was enough.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:12.89,2:40:16.67,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,希望这至少让你觉得\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}I hope that at least in your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,2:40:17.41,2:40:21.27,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有辜负你们为我做的一切\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}l've earned what all of you have done for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:34.71,2:40:36.23,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}James.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:38.22,2:40:40.99,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,“约翰米勒上尉”\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}"Captain John H. Miller."
Dialogue: 0,2:40:48.98,2:40:53.59,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说我这辈子没白活     什么\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}- Tell me I have led a good life.   - What?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:54.16,2:40:56.41,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说，我是个好人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}Tell me I'm a good mess.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:03.52,2:41:05.48,对白,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好人\N{\fs49\fnWin7 YaHei\shad2\c&H849F7F&}You are.
